      in just <br><br><b>4 DAYS</b> at<br><br>Homewood Teaching Academy
    </h1>
    <br>
    <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
      <h2 class="container">
          <span class=""><b> $11 per hour:</b> Minimum wage that non-certified instructors in Tahoe make their first season</span>
          <br>
          <span class=""><b> $17 per hour:</b> Base rate for Snow Schoolers instructors (plus tips and incentive-based bonuses!)</span>
